Package: scTSS
Type: Package
Title: Study transcription start site (TSS) by 5' scRNA-seq data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Shiwei Fu <shiwei.fu@email.ucr.edu>, Wei Vivian Li <weil@ucr.edu>
Maintainer: Shiwei Fu <shiwei.fu@email.ucr.edu>
Description: A toolkit for predicting and quantifying TSS clusters based on 5' single-cell RNA-seq data and conducting differential TSS usage tests between conditions.
